The course give overview about the concept of health, the main indicators of health behavior, healthy lifestyle and risk behavior, health education possibilities, and main principles of providing first aid.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of course is to provide overview about the concept of health, the main indicators on health behavior, the factors influencing the health status and possibilities for health promotion.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Student. 1) describes the health concept and main indicators of health behavior in Estonia 2) analyzes the relationships between lifestyle and health, and can describe the possibilities to prevent risk behavior 3) describes the general prevention possibilities for main health problems 3) knows the main principles of first aid
